de" class="qkw">KAKA</a>都是四号位，加上阵容指挥等问题，NewBee这套阵容还有待磨合和考验。</p><p><img src="http://p34.qhimg.com/t0101aa0ede64ecfe8c.jpg?size=550x209"></p><p>不过有趣的是在今天早些时候，<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=CDEC&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">CDEC</a>战队的三号位Xz发表微博,表示已经离开CDEC转会Y队,Ti5的奇迹之师光辉不再。加上之前NewBee老板狗徒在微博因XZ怒喷LGD，也许意味着NewBee刚刚好和LGD谈妥转会条件，小智或许就顺理成章的加入了NewBee。</p><p><img src="http://p32.qhimg.com/t01fcbd18b25a47c881.jpg?size=829x341"></p><p>点击查看大图</p></div>  <footer>  <p class=tip_quick>文章内容由搜索引擎自动发现并显示为快照，不代表360新闻的立场和观点，<a target=_blank class=viewsource href="http://games.ifeng.com/a/20160318/41564959_0.shtml">查看原文</a></p>      </footer> </article> <section class=sohu_cy> <div id=SOHUCS sid='12f1d137db54eb9c2892110ac4c2b7e6'></div><script id=changyan_mobile_js charset="utf-8" src="http://changyan.sohu.com/upload/mobile/wap-js/changyan_mobile.js?client_id=cyrTywwWs&conf=prod_c56aa5a54e89138d855c5ca9b31470a0" ></script> </section>  <aside id="next-news"> <h3><em>狗哥</em>的其它新闻:</h3> <ul>    <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E7%8B%97%E5%93%A5&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=2&amp;m=b0e259a59cc6935bfd34569c060da722e652da1b&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.comnews.cn%2Fn%2Fyl%2F2016-03-21%2F3812.html" data-pos="1"> <b>狗哥</b>姜GARY叫板《我们相爱吧》橙汁夫妇 曝宋智孝睡觉美颜称周一情侣才是真爱 </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E7%8B%97%E5%93%A5&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=3&amp;m=dcc66d69c7dd814f6f520535ab0b6286e1d7319a&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fcnews.chinadaily.com.cn%2F2016-03%2F08%2Fcontent_23785761.htm" data-pos="2"> <b>狗哥</b>gary巡演北京站3月26日举行 今日正式开票 </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E7%8B%97%E5%93%A5&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=4&amp;m=f046692677705f014bfd0b14af129139b7f3afdb&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fcnews.chinadaily.com.cn%2F2016-03%2F08%2Fcontent_23785536.htm" data-pos="3"> <b>狗哥</b>gary3月26日登京开唱 分享经典感动夜 </a>  </ul> </aside>  <div class=mask style="display:none"></div> <div class="open-in-browser-tip" style="display:none"> <p>好无奈，微信君不让直接下载，别担心，点击<b>右上角</b>，选择“<b>在浏览器中打开</b>”就能下载啦~</p> <a class=close href="javascript:;"><img src="http://p3.qhimg.com/d/inn/a8960a66/close.png"></